esmanager (1.3-4) stable; urgency=medium

  * Implemented interrupted downloads resumption
  * Custom mod's path selector was returned
  * "Incomplete" page added
  * Added download percents displaying in mod-bars for corresponding states
  * Fixed bug with vote unavailability for new mods
  * Fixed distortions while help showing
  * Fixed crash by memory exhaustion during mod highspeed downloading

 --  Alexander S. Salieff <salieff@mail.ru>  Thu, 09 Feb 2017 18:42:22 +0300

esmanager (1.2-0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Improved mod's path finding algorithms for Android

 --  Alexander S. Salieff <salieff@mail.ru>  Mon, 03 Oct 2016 03:10:26 +0300

esmanager (1.1-11) stable; urgency=medium

  * Implemented filter for Installed / All / Not installed mod-lists as 3-page swipe panel
  * Implemented scrollbar marker for mod-lists
  * Implemented displaying of installations statistics and mod's lifetime in rating window
  * Added sort by active / total installations and life-time
  * Improved sort by score
  * Implemented correct work on new iOS versions
  * User-Agent from Nexus 5 used for network requests to avoid inaccessibility of download
  * Implemented autosearch mods path for Android as for iOS, removed manual mods path selection possibility
  * Accelerated scores and statistics loading during the launch
  * For server-side corrupted mods (404, etc) status "Failed" displayed instantaneously
  * Timestamps added to clipboard begin for log and traceback copying
  * Fixed processing of archives which contain files with absolute paths
  * Fixed processing of archives which contain directories with non-zero sizes
  * Fixed inability to display help for iOS users
  * Minimal Android version increased to 4.1 according to Qt 5.7
  * Initial support for user identificaton by UDID instead of MAC address

 --  Alexander S. Salieff <salieff@mail.ru>  Mon, 03 Oct 2016 03:10:26 +0300

